Virat Kohli Cricket Stats Dashboard
This project presents an interactive dashboard to analyze Virat Kohli's cricket statistics, providing insights into his performance across different formats, matches, and conditions.

Project Overview:
The dashboard visualizes key performance metrics, helping cricket enthusiasts, analysts, and fans explore Kohliâ€™s stats in an interactive way.

Features & Insights:

Batting Performance:

Total runs, average, and strike rate across Tests, ODIs, and T20s , IPL.

Centuries & Half-Centuries.

Total number of 100s & 50s by format.

Breakdown of centuries across different years.

Runs by year and format Analysis.

Technologies Used:

Python (Data Processing)
Pandas & NumPy (Data Cleaning & Transformation)
POWER BI (Data Visualization)
POWER BI(Interactive Dashboard)
